metadata.name: Intergalactic
metadata.description:
Intergalactic is a journey charting to the unknown.
A combination of stars separated from their birth cluster, black holes and gas clouds. 

All important factors play a vital life cycle for new stars to be born. A conquest into a curiosity for the treasures we've still yet to find.

Rare Edition: 1/1
Dimensions: 6000px x 4000px
Adobe: Photoshop
